{"tid":464412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又來！重建地盤　工人墮𨋢槽 昏迷送院","createTime":"2017-11-10T13:28:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T14:53:31.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"afbe5e19151dfec008774fedc51c2d48d7f65d10","tid":464412,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:28:22.000Z","msg":"尖沙嘴一個地盤發生工業意外。傍晚約6時，梳士巴利道新世界中心重建地盤內，一個工人在5至6樓間的𨋢槽維修時，突然被升降機夾着困住，救援人員接報後趕往現場。消防坍塌拯救隊亦到場協助，目前仍在拯救中。肇事工人約六時許被困，個多小時後始獲救出，送院搶救，接近八時，他被送入醫院，送院時昏迷，救護人員一直為他進行心外壓，其後情況好轉，送往急切治療部救治。工友亦趕至醫院了解。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，傷者姓孫，49歲，為迅達電梯公司駐地盤的維修升降機工人，今日到地盤維修升降機，出事後大聲呼救，工友循聲尋獲，馬上報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/132579/尖沙嘴新世界重建地盤-工人墮𨋢槽近兩小時獲救-昏迷送院\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F132579%2F%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%98%B4%E6%96%B0%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%87%8D%E5%BB%BA%E5%9C%B0%E7%9B%A4-%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E5%A2%AE%F0%A8%8B%A2%E6%A7%BD%E8%BF%91%E5%85%A9%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E7%8D%B2%E6%95%91-%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7%E9%80%81%E9%99%A2&d=blywfIoetm%2BjvA%2F6sN2iB%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=fe9eec69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/132579/尖沙嘴新世界重建地盤-工人墮𨋢槽近兩小時獲救-昏迷送院</a>"},{"pid":"8f8af05b5ecc21da54672b8d6338ac8cb18a30fe","tid":464412,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:29:10.000Z","msg":"返工=??"},{"pid":"7fe439db3a795c85c52d141b48dfe8f1ee494d06","tid":464412,"uid":21306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工=??</blockquote><br />\n不了"},{"pid":"39a4a1ca67fc7e31266451d2beb5582dba25d141","tid":464412,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:40:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>返工=??</blockquote><br />\n不了</blockquote><br />\nX3"},{"pid":"f3c14f486aa8bb04916fa09fd996d67cf2c0cb4e","tid":464412,"uid":139720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:44:30.000Z","msg":"死撚緊"},{"pid":"4cf1144c3a799c24737cd63bf278aa91880ef927","tid":464412,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"呢估地盤之前又有一單"},{"pid":"9e900fc1f793fbb71eb8f214a1f9e5bcc189b54f","tid":464412,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:04:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢估地盤之前又有一單</blockquote><br />\n地盤過去亦曾發生多次工業意外。上月17日，一名男工人在上址進行拆卸工作期間，頸部動脈意外被物件割傷，血流如注。其中在2014年2月，14年2月，一名工人協助吊臂車將一條工字鐵吊下車時，鐵鏈疑突然斷裂，工字鐵砸落地面，工人被擊中，昏迷送院不治。<br />\n<br />\n新世界中心重建工程在2013年啟動，將重建為「Victoria Dockside」，預計2019年全面落成啟用，項目投資26億美元（約202.8億港元），提供300萬平方呎總樓面。"},{"pid":"920c827255a2f37956f215a8c18128d6606c7d81","tid":464412,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:30:01.000Z","msg":"做lift真係搵命搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d04c9213afcdc6c9921f5da2f08806de9ea0d89","tid":464412,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:46:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37f752c8e59617a00d5784dc6a7e9d0f45404331","tid":464412,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"cbc43f3ff298d3de57379220bf1837ee53fa4bd2","tid":464412,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T14:53:31.000Z","msg":"好彩有人返工<br />\n條友先可以尋求到協助<br />\n接受到治療<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返工=好嘢"}]}